Name: Bouncing Duck Simulator
About the game: Bouncing Duck Simulator allows you to fulfill your wildest dreams. Bouncing a rubber duck around, bouncing a pink rubber duck around, bouncing... more ducks? Don't be shy, you gotta bounce them all! The game features: - A room made of 6 walls, allowing for crazy bouncing action! - Three differents endings and hidden techniques/achievements, for a great replayability! - A wide range of collectable ducks that you have to find to complete the Duckedex to 100%! - Many duck combinations and non-linear gameplay, every playthrough is unique! - Various duck sounds that will haunt you for days (months), even during your sleep! Bounce your way to the ultimate title of Master Bouncer!
